com.dlsc.flexgantt.model.gantt

Interface ISpreadsheetValuesList

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    SpreadsheetValuesList

    public interface ISpreadsheetValuesList
    A data structure used to store references between time spans and objects. This list comes in very handy in combination with spreadsheets. The application can set and retrieve objects based on a time span. If an object is associated with a certain time span and another object gets associated with a time span that is contained within the first time span, then the list will be splitted (fragmented). Fragmentation only happens when new values are added to the list, not when they are retrieved.
    Since:
    2.1
    Author:
    Dirk Lemmermann
